{"tid":1362831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"外國勢力入侵！泰國拳手認受僱參與元朗恐襲 襲擊市民！","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:06:43.000Z","uid":88215,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3738797f72b1a616c9b02acd42c0eb51c1ee9e","tid":1362831,"uid":88215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"泰國新聞已經陸續報道，路透社也發佈了新聞，34歲泰國前泰拳拳手旅居香港十多年，受雇在元朗西地鐵站持棍暴打香港示威市民。<br />\n該名泰國前拳手坦言受雇到元朗與一大批黑社會聯手暴打示威人群，新聞視頻在泰國播出後被泰國觀眾認出其身份，泰國記者追問該拳手時，他坦言受雇行事。<br />\n泰國人民痛心竟然有泰國人在香港行暴，嚴重傷害兩地情感，並向香港人道歉。<br />\n<br />\n泰國新聞post: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/159005400803388/posts/2519677174736187?s=100000947229001&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F159005400803388%2Fposts%2F2519677174736187%3Fs%3D100000947229001%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=01a1eef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/159005400803388/posts/2519677174736187?s=100000947229001&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TRoDsWz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTRoDsWz.png&h=75d87c12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"027ed5b2bbdfa09d997a594a2ab1f6786dfa53e2","tid":1362831,"uid":88215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"ecd3fd7d9ece737958118e9ff7e3e74b7de8b747","tid":1362831,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8834934f354961eca47c5665cc57f11ffd0a8f38","tid":1362831,"uid":148104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"220d330f020414bc367e5e752ad792bd98cc7cb7","tid":1362831,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:04:50.000Z","msg":"認左咁幾時受審坐監？"},{"pid":"dbf565cb42c9566c1cf9fea990a45955674cd508","tid":1362831,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislik